# Page & Section Patterns

Full docs: `docs/design-system/patterns.md` and `docs/design-system/composites.md`

## Page Structure

- List/pipeline pages: use `PrimaryPageTemplate`.
- Dashboard/overview: compose `MapSection`, `KeyMetricsShowcase`, `PendingApprovalChartCard`, `AlertsSection`.
- Section wrapper: `px-4 lg:px-6 space-y-4`; `gap-12` between sections.

## Key Metrics — Full Width, No Margins

- `KeyMetricsShowcase` must be full width with no horizontal margins.
- Do not add margin-left, margin-right, or wrapper margins. Keep padding (`px-4 lg:px-6`) inside the component.

## Page Scroll

- **List pages** (DataTable): default — only tab content scrolls.
- **Content pages** (Reports, dashboard-style sections): `fullPageScroll` — whole page scrolls as one unit.
- Do not add `overflow-auto` to tab content when using `fullPageScroll`.

## Tabs — Consistent Pattern

- `TabsList`: `flex-nowrap w-max` (or `w-fit`)
- `TabsTrigger`: icon + label (+ optional Badge for counts)
- `TabsContent`: `m-0`; add `pt-6` for content spacing

## Report Tabs (ReportPageTemplate)

- **Underline variant:** `TabsList` bg-transparent, `TabsTrigger` border-b-2, active = border-primary
- **Config:** `ReportPageViewConfig` — name, id, icon, optional description (tooltip), optional count
- **Labels:** Dashboard, Analytics, Charts, Media, Reports (semantic names)

## Sections

- Use `SectionWithHeader` — don't build custom section headers.
- `variant="withFilter"` when a filter (Select, etc.) appears on the right.

## Metrics

- Use `KeyMetricsShowcase` for metric grids with optional insight card.
- Ratio: ~70% metrics, ~30% insight when both present.

## Charts

- Use `PendingApprovalChartCard` for bar, pie, donut, line, area charts.
- Use Recharts with `ResponsiveContainer`; chart-token colors only.
